TI  - Cu2+ coordination-induced in situ photo-to- heat on catalytic sites to hydrolyze β-lactam antibiotics pollutants in waters
PY  - 2023
T2  - Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America
VL  - 120
IS  - 52
